                    <h3>How do I pay for a CyberMall purchase?</h3>
                    <p>We offer you various payment methods to choose from. We prioritize the security and confidentiality of your transaction details and partner with trusted payment gateways that use secure encryption technology.</p>

                    <h3>Payment Methods</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Internet Banking</li>
                        <li>Gift Card</li>
                        <li>Cash on Delivery (COD)</li>
                        <li>Wallet</li>
                        <li>Credit/Debit Cards</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3>Internet Banking</h3>
                    <p>You can pay through your bank's online banking facility. We accept payments from various banks in India and other countries.</p>

                    <h3>Gift Card</h3>
                    <p>You can use CyberMall gift cards to make purchases on our website.</p>

                    <h3>Cash on Delivery (COD)</h3>
                    <p>If you are not comfortable making an online payment, you can choose the Cash on Delivery option. With COD, you can pay in cash at the time of delivery of the product at your doorstep.</p>
                    <p>Please note that the maximum order value for COD payments is â‚¹50,000, and it is strictly a cash-only payment method. Foreign currency and gift cards cannot be used for COD orders.</p>

                    <h3>Wallet</h3>
                    <p>You can use your CyberMall Wallet to make purchases on our website. You can add money to your wallet using various payment methods like debit card, credit card, net banking, and UPI.</p>

                    <h4>Credit/Debit Cards</h4>
                    <p>We accept payments made using Visa, MasterCard, Maestro, and American Express credit/debit cards issued in India and other countries.</p>
                    <h3>What measures does CyberMall take to ensure the security of online transactions on their website?</h3>
                    <p>We ensure that all your online transactions on CyberMall are secure and protected. We use 256-bit encryption technology to protect your card information while transmitting it to the respective banks for payment processing. All credit card and debit card payments on CyberMall are processed through secure and trusted payment gateways managed by leading banks.</p>
                    <p>We also continuously monitor transactions for suspicious activity and flag potentially fraudulent transactions for manual verification by our team. In rare cases, when our team is unable to rule out the possibility of fraud categorically, the transaction is kept on hold, and the customer is requested to provide identity documents. We apologize for any inconvenience that may be caused to customers and request them to bear with us in the larger interest of ensuring a safe and secure environment for online transactions.</p>
                    <h3>Does CyberMall charge any hidden fees or taxes for their products?</h3>
                    <p>We do not charge any hidden fees or taxes for our products. The prices listed for all the items are final and all-inclusive. However, delivery charges may be extra depending on the seller policy. Please check the individual seller for the same.</p>
                    <p>Thank you for choosing CyberMall for your online shopping needs!</p>
               
                
